<div class="title">A Unique Feeling</div>
<div class="substance">Modafinil (Provigil) & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=provsrock&Exact=1">provsrock</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; provsrock. "A Unique Feeling: An Experience with Modafinil (Provigil) & Alcohol (exp38043)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 12, 2004. erowid.org/exp/38043</div>

<br/>



